                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d602">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/17525</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Representative <persName type="from"
                            >Rodgers</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Querètaro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-03-18T18:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 18, 1916, 6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s March 15, 1 p.m., to Belt, only received 10 o’clock, 18th.</p>
                <p>Matter taken up at once with War Department. Am informed there is now complete
                    understanding between Mexican and American forces. Everything proceeding
                    satisfactorily.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Rodgers</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
